# AI Context Rules
- Always prioritize context from `./graphify-out/graph.json` before reading raw source files.
- Use Graphify graph queries to trace relationships between modules.
- Refer to `./graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` for a high-level architectural overview.
- Rebuild graph when structure changes with: `C:\Users\Rohan\AppData\Local\Python\pythoncore-3.14-64\Scripts\graphify.exe update .`
- Use package/tool name `graphifyy` when installing via pip.
